Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:36.00,Title,Sign 0033,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,256)}Reunion in the Den of Evil
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.46,0:02:06.49,Default,Knights,0000,0000,0000,,It's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:08.29,Default,Knights,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:11.32,Default - italics,F,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Swordsman...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.61,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting out of here, Isidoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:15.67,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure those two get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.67,0:02:17.36,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,Right! You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:19.67,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,I found an escape route in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:21.63,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:23.12,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,I charge high interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:25.24,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Save the talk for after we get out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:31.00,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.88,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,I bet I broke the sound barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:36.87,Default,Knights,0000,0000,0000,,It appears they're fighting off heretics.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:39.93,Default,Azan,0000,0000,0000,,That does not mean they are our allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.18,Default,Knights,0000,0000,0000,,Have you all forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:43.39,Default,Knights,0000,0000,0000,,He's taken the lives of our comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:44.63,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:47.52,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,Should we also capture the Black \NSwordsman, Lady Farnese?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:49.39,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,That will not be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:53.35,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,We are in the midst of battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.35,0:02:55.90,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,Kill all who do not offer their surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.57,Default,Azan,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Farnese, if I may...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:58.24,Default,Azan,0000,0000,0000,,We are to take the Black Swordsman alive—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:02:58.96,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:02.97,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,If we do not act, we shall only \Nsuffer more casualties!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:05.47,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,There is no doubt they are heretics.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:07.87,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,Annihilate them, along with the Black Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:11.25,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,We have pledged our swords to God. \NWe cannot allow ourselves to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:13.38,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,All troops, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:17.20,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,So, fight fire with fire, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:18.25,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:19.04,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:22.72,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Show us the way, Isidoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:23.96,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:24.94,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,Do not let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:25.79,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Farnese!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:28.97,Default - italics,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:30.73,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,It's up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:42.84,Default - Apostle,Goat,0000,0000,0000,,Won't let you have witch...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:45.28,Default - Apostle,Goat,0000,0000,0000,,Consummate... Mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:47.03,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:04.73,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,Without Godo's armor, my spine \Nwould've been snapped in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:10.81,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Make him into goat stew!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.69,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Isidoro, take those two and go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:14.73,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:17.14,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving Casca to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:21.96,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.24,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:24.87,Default - Apostle,Goat,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.62,Default - Apostle,Goat,0000,0000,0000,,Leave her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:39.84,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,You keep forcing Casca away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.29,0:04:42.93,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,You're like a half-Apostle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:47.34,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,I guess your being here means there's some \Ntruth to the old skeleton's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:48.81,Default - Apostle,Goat,0000,0000,0000,,Kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:50.49,Default - Apostle,Goat,0000,0000,0000,,Trample you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:52.35,Default - Apostle,Goat,0000,0000,0000,,Skewer you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:57.18,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't leave her behind\Nin such a foul place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:02.22,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll take her with me for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:24.21,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like one or two arrows have no effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:28.68,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll give this a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:34.35,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:35.71,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.02,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:06.63,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,These explosive bombs aren't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:23.36,Default,Azan,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Farnese,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:25.16,Default,Azan,0000,0000,0000,,in this chaos, it is too dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for our commander to endanger \Nher own person in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:32.24,Default,Azan,0000,0000,0000,,Please retreat to the cave entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:33.25,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:34.26,Default,Azan,0000,0000,0000,,Escort the commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:34.96,Default,Knights,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:36.22,Default,Knights,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Lady Farnese.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:36.74,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,Azan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:38.50,Default,Azan,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:40.95,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:42.83,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Officer of Arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:44.63,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,Serpico, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.76,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they didn't fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:04.65,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,I have been waiting for you, Black Swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:06.71,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.55,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:21.22,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,That was uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:25.72,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:28.21,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to me right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:30.59,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:32.84,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no path!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:37.00,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,Were the heretics planning to escape \Nby jumping off or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.71,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,What now, monkey pants?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:39.73,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:43.18,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:44.29,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,With this, we're golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:45.82,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:47.23,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:48.68,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:49.96,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lower the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.27,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,Just like lowering boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:52.49,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.03,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't work for you, jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.24,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:57.79,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,This lady's the problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:00.00,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting sucked in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:10.38,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:15.21,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,On principle, I prevent people \Nfrom drawing their weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:19.11,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, you can't swing \Nthat sword of yours here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:21.59,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.32,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,I made the right choice, getting ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:28.08,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,To think I'd chance upon such \Nperfect terrain to fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:31.40,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose this might be a sign of God's grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:32.44,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,Above all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:37.52,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to overwhelm you with \Nsheer numbers is madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:41.81,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,If you can cut down ten men with that sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:44.36,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,it's enough to change the tide \Nof battle in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:49.41,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,Allies infected by fear are even \Nworse foes than the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:51.53,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,He's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:54.43,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even get a chance to draw my blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:59.63,Default - italics,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,You provoke our Lady Farnese a bit too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:01.46,Default - italics,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get rid of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:17.21,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:18.72,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:20.35,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look down...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.71,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:29.92,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I reached the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:34.44,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.40,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:39.57,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,All right, don't struggle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:53.74,Default - italics,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,The westward sun, shining in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:57.03,Default - italics,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,The cramped, unstable footing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:59.08,Default - italics,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,Your hulking body, encumbered by armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.08,0:10:01.41,Default - italics,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,Your sword arm, made useless by the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:04.29,Default - italics,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,They all serve to shackle you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:06.28,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,He's not just a glib talker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:08.50,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,He's highly skilled with his sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:12.12,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,His attacks are so versatile, \NI can't predict them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:15.47,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,He's a far more challenging foe \Nthan that half-Apostle earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:21.30,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I can't waste time here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:26.04,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worried about those girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:29.48,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,My comrades are waiting for them up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.09,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they have already \Nbeen taken into custody!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:36.40,Default - italics,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,That's a total bluff...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.82,Default - italics,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,I need you even more on edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:42.32,Default - italics,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can win in a fair fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:54.67,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,How foolhardy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:57.42,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Fool? Not as much as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:00.93,Default,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to pull back my blade, \Nyour fingers would—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:07.28,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,I have my reflexes. And my strong arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:10.19,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I have really thick skin on my palms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:36.58,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect him to dodge like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:39.05,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, he moves like a pickpocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:42.01,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,His quick wits let him use a \Nweapon he's only seen once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:48.37,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,He's more cunning than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.81,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,Like a fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:12:00.47,Default - italics,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't do things so out of character...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:06.92,Default - italics,Ser,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's unlike me to get so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:13.40,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,With this many men,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:15.88,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,how could you fail to capture \Nthe Black Swordsman,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:19.04,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,much less prevent him from entering the cave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:20.63,Default,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,I am deeply sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:22.76,Default,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,We were taken by surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:25.68,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,I shan't tolerate excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:34.83,Default,Jerome,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty unhinged...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:38.27,Default,Jerome,0000,0000,0000,,And her flunky's nowhere to be seen, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:54.22,Default,Jerome,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:55.27,Default,Joachim,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:56.69,Default,Joachim,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought I saw something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:10.80,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:12.38,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.31,Default,Joachim,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:21.25,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Joachim...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:25.33,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:27.07,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Did they find us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:29.99,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Joachim, you're alive—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:33.98,Default,Joachim,0000,0000,0000,,Heretics!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:36.12,Default,Joachim,0000,0000,0000,,There are heretics behind those rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.00,Default,Knights,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:40.28,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Joachim...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:44.30,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, lady! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:46.34,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,If you stand there, they'll catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:49.19,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Casca?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:00.43,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, Isidoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:05.78,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:17.65,Default,Knights,0000,0000,0000,,Commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:20.54,Default,Knights,0000,0000,0000,,our work to quell the heretics \Nis nearly complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.52,Default,F,0000,0000,0000,,What of the Black Swordsman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:25.41,Default,Knights,0000,0000,0000,,He has not been seen among \Nthe captured or the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:28.55,Default,Knights,0000,0000,0000,,Walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:31.28,Default - italics,F,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:34.09,Default - italics,F,0000,0000,0000,,The one the Black Knight leapt to save.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:46.81,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:36.14,Default,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:38.40,Default,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,If we haven't returned by morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.91,Default,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,you have to leave Albion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:44.92,Default,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,If you dawdle, the officials \Nwill find you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.03,Default,Pepe,0000,0000,0000,,Luca...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:50.23,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,You should change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:53.23,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,I can't guarantee your survival, \Nand you'll hold me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:55.02,Default,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,My, so negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:58.65,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this isn't a job for a lady, Luca!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:15:59.98,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,That goes for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:02.36,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing this for my own reasons!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.76,Default - italics,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make up for my mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:09.24,Default,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't on top of my game earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:10.99,Default,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,but that'll change this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:15.16,Default,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't the only one who's worried \Nabout those girls, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:19.50,Default,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, the monastery owes me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:22.21,Default,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on how it goes, \Nwe might avoid bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:24.46,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:26.51,Default,Fuque,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it'll work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:28.10,Default,Lucy,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:32.57,Default,Fuque,0000,0000,0000,,I think they should give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:35.42,Default,Fuque,0000,0000,0000,,Once someone's inside that tower, \Nthere's nothing to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:40.30,Default,Lucy,0000,0000,0000,,Luca's so stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:43.03,Default,Lucy,0000,0000,0000,,She's way too responsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:48.41,Default,Fuque,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do if they don't come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:50.36,Default,Lucy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:55.97,Default - italics,Pepe,0000,0000,0000,,Please return Luca and everyone \Nsafely to us, oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:57.87,Default - italics,Pepe,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:01.09,Default - italics,Pepe,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:07.88,Default - Apostle,Skele,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A shadow will be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:15.51,Default - Apostle,Skele,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It will simply be a shadow cast by a dying \Nsun that shines on a faraway land.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:21.13,Default - Apostle,Skele,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(1,882)}We are already caught in the whorls of karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:26.50,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:28.16,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I lost them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:31.17,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,With so many people here, I can \Nbarely sense their presences.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:32.20,Default,Knights,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:33.13,Default,Knights,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:34.81,Default,Knights,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I saw something there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:36.28,Default,Knights,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you saw a bat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.33,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm still visible,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:40.60,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,even in this giant temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:44.20,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, why is it so hard to breathe here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:47.65,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a lair of demonic creatures? \NEven that wouldn't explain all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:49.54,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Many things are much more sinister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:51.62,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I have a really bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:54.05,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I need to find the girls soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:05.74,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:08.03,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Help, Luca...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:14.11,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Elaine, aren't you a witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:16.82,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we use your witchcraft to escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:20.72,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:23.59,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't escape soon, we'll be in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:29.21,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:33.93,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever... I don't care anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:35.80,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,It's all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:38.30,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Since you came into my life, \Nnothing good has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.16,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Only horrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:43.35,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I took care of you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:45.35,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,But look at me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:47.54,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,always happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:55.73,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:57.44,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:18:59.92,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Elaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.41,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:08.57,Default,Dwarf,0000,0000,0000,,One of you, out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:14.54,Default,Dwarf,0000,0000,0000,,Don't care who.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:15.86,Default,Dwarf,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.93,0:19:19.13,Default,Dwarf,0000,0000,0000,,You, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:20.62,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Elaine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:23.58,Default,Dwarf,0000,0000,0000,,You, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:25.39,Default,Dwarf,0000,0000,0000,,I choose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:28.87,Default,Dwarf,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend was getting taken away,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:30.64,Default,Dwarf,0000,0000,0000,,but you didn't try to help her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:33.05,Default,Dwarf,0000,0000,0000,,You only thought of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:35.61,Default,Dwarf,0000,0000,0000,,I hate cowards like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:36.95,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.15,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:40.69,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.69,0:19:42.41,Default,Dwarf,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.45,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Elaine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:44.72,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:51.34,Default - italics,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:54.75,Default - italics,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Is it my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:56.74,Default - italics,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Am I the one who's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:19:59.29,Default - italics,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:01.01,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:09.46,Default - italics,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to live, even if it meant \Nabandoning half-witted Elaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:14.80,Default - italics,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm like this and may die soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.85,Default - italics,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's why I want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:23.07,Default - italics,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:27.02,Default - italics,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,God is punishing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:31.66,Default,Dwarf,0000,0000,0000,,Our investigations revealed \Nthere is an actual witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:35.12,Default,Dwarf,0000,0000,0000,,We've looked into all the other women.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:38.00,Default,Dwarf,0000,0000,0000,,One of you is the witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:40.02,Default - italics,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,He's talking about Elaine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:44.30,Default - italics,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,If I tell him everything now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:46.58,Default - italics,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,maybe they won't hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:48.48,Default - italics,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,If I tell him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:53.28,Default - italics,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, everyone looks out for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:57.03,Default - flashback,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,No way will I abandon anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:20:58.89,Default - flashback,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Not you or Elaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:01.43,Default - italics,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Luca...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:07.33,Default - italics,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:10.62,Default - italics,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I only need a tiny bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:14.62,Default - italics,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Just a small part of your courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:35.24,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.24,0:21:36.85,Default,Dwarf,0000,0000,0000,,Just walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:40.90,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:43.41,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:46.45,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:48.97,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Luca!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.28,0:22:00.66,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.66,0:22:03.13,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,It's ridiculously big up close!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.13,0:22:05.92,Default,Ishi,0000,0000,0000,,More like a fortress than a holy temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:08.16,Default,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.16,0:22:10.03,Default,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your voice down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:10.96,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:13.68,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,My brand's throbbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:15.62,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,An Apostle?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:16.95,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.37,0:22:18.44,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,more monstrous than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.59,0:22:21.07,Default - italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,There's something very wrong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.95,0:24:01.42,Title,Sign 2404,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.42,0:24:05.42,EndInsert,Sign 2404,0000,0000,0000,,I have witnessed a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.17,0:24:09.51,EndInsert,Sign 2408,0000,0000,0000,,I have found that faith means death!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.47,0:24:13.47,EndInsert,Sign 2412,0000,0000,0000,,Fool, you seek to rebel against God!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.47,0:24:17.47,EndInsert,Sign 2416,0000,0000,0000,,Impertinent witch!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.48,0:24:21.48,EndInsert,Sign 2420,0000,0000,0000,,I will have you atone with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.92,0:24:27.54,Title2,Sign 2425,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode \NBlood Flow of the Dead
